These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, october
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, ebony
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Nationality         | egyptian | indonesian  |
| Birthday       | october    | july    |
| Color   | ebony       | pink      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
There are 2 different nationalities: french, italian
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, black
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana
1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the french is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Nationality           | french | italian      |
| Color   | black  | yellow      |
| Cigar         | oliveros | havana     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, red
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, may
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Color          | blood-red    | red   |
| Flower   | dahlia  | amaryllis   |
| Birthday     | may     | july |

