.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia
There 2 different types of food: spinach, blueberry
House: victorian, townhouse
1. the coach is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the coach is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the person eating spinach is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Flower   | begonia          | dahlia |
| Food           | spinach          | blueberry    |
| House     | townhouse            | victorian       |

 